Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.05,0:00:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是御伽银行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.90,0:00:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实地束手就擒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.76,0:00:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再纠缠她了  听清楚了没有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.83,0:00:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则这些照片会全部送到你老家和警察那里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.28,0:00:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.10,0:00:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林檎  你退后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.80,0:00:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.29,0:00:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少瞧不起人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.72,0:01:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一辈子都别起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.52,0:01:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  真不愧是凉子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.53,0:01:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经漂亮地录下来了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.82,0:01:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.18,0:01:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  林檎  刚才...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.74,0:01:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.42,0:01:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  没什么
